board retreat offer
Home
Offers
Board Retreat Offer
board retreat Offer
Reserve your next board retreat with us and receive the following perks:
100% Ocean View Beach Houses with full kitchen, living room, dining room and two full bathrooms
Built in teambuilding activities with on-site watersports and charter fishing
Private Pool/Courtyard available for Cocktail Receptions
Enjoy fine dining in Butterfly Cafe
Complimentary welcome amenity for all
$75.00 Resort Credit per guest room
Offer subject to availability and not combinable with any other offer. For more information or to book, contact
[email protected]
.
In order to qualify for group offer, group must have a minimum of 20 total room nights (4 rooms x 5 nights or 3 rooms x 7 nights etc.)
